query:
select
                users.username,
                count(links.dest_bookmark_id) as "linked_bookmark_count!",
                count(links.dest_list_id) as "linked_list_count!"
            from lists
            join users on lists.user_id = users.id
            left join links
                on lists.id = links.src_list_id
            where lists.id = $1
            group by users.username, users.email
